<p>Speaking of which, Gera@Sweet Foods, the chocolatier of whom I write serves a chilled chocolate in summer.  It&#8217;s slightly lighter and the chocolate does go a bit grainy but I love it anyway.  I suggest you give chilling a try.</p>
